es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.util

Enum JOctomapLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<JOctomapLogger>
      • es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.util.JOctomapLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<JOctomapLogger>

    public enum JOctomapLogger
extends Enum<JOctomapLogger>
    Custom class to extend the capabilities of Logger for the JOctomap library. This class enables an interface to call logger features without using the Logger.getLogger(String) method in all calls.
    Author:
    Adrián González Sieira <adrian.gonzalez@usc.es>
